p-block-group is-style-block-section has-myrgroup-gray-dark-color has-white-background-color has-text-color has-background\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover has-background-dim is-style-left-image-content\" id=\"learn-more\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1536\" class=\"wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-1865\" alt=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/Comerford-18-Substation-2021-2-26-9.jpg\" style=\"object-position:38% 84%\" data-object-fit=\"cover\" data-object-position=\"38% 84%\" srcset=\"https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/Comerford-18-Substation-2021-2-26-9.jpg 2048w, https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/Comerford-18-Substation-2021-2-26-9-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/Comerford-18-Substation-2021-2-26-9-1600x1200.jpg 1600w, https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/Comerford-18-Substation-2021-2-26-9-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/Comerford-18-Substation-2021-2-26-9-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" \/><div class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-cover-is-layout-flow\">\n<h2 class=\"is-style-has-underline wp-block-heading\">Delivering optimal, turnkey substation solutions&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Working side-by-side with our clients, we anticipate needs and deliver innovative solutions to ensure superior project execution. Our proven track record boasts successful project management and construction of high-voltage substations, switching stations, and interconnect stations ranging from 34.5kV to 765kV. This unmatched experience provides value, knowledge, and comprehensive solutions for our clients and partners.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>As one of the nation\u2019s largest and most established electrical contractors, our suite of electrical construction services provides our clients with complete turnkey services, including project management support, material procurement and management, quality assurance\/quality control (QA\/QC), outstanding safety performance, testing and commissioning, and final job closeout.<\/p>\n\n\n\n\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-style-block-section\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover has-background-dim is-style-right-image-content\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1152\" class=\"wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-1678\" alt=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Image-2-GSWC-Dallas-Ft-Worth-003-2.jpg\" data-object-fit=\"cover\" srcset=\"https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Image-2-GSWC-Dallas-Ft-Worth-003-2.jpg 2048w, https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Image-2-GSWC-Dallas-Ft-Worth-003-2-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Image-2-GSWC-Dallas-Ft-Worth-003-2-1600x900.jpg 1600w, https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Image-2-GSWC-Dallas-Ft-Worth-003-2-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Image-2-GSWC-Dallas-Ft-Worth-003-2-1536x864.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" \/><div class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-cover-is-layout-flow\">\n<h2 class=\"is-style-has-underline has-black-color has-text-color wp-block-heading\">Properly positioned for long-term success<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Our customers expect superior project execution, and we strive always to deliver to these standards. From collector systems and switchyards, to engineering and bus work, our subsidiaries\u2019 extensive expertise, skill set, and resources help bring any project vision to life. Our teams are versed in performing substation work under engineer-procure-construct (EPC) and construct-only methods of project delivery and our vast experience spans decades and hundreds of substation projects.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>We work closely with clients to take a comprehensive approach to planning, executing, and commissioning on every project. This collaboration has enabled us to build strong, long-standing relationships and performance partnerships with our valued clients.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group mb-md-5\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\"><div class=\"wp-block-myrgroup-homepage-carousel\">\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"is-style-has-underline\">See what we&#039;re capable of<\/h3>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"carousel\">\r\n\r\n    <div class=\"slide\">\r\n    <a href=\"https:\/\/exiinc.com\/projects\/sloan-canyon-switchyard-and-transmission-line\/\">\r\n      <figure>\r\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1066\" src=\"https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Sloan-Canyon-Project-15-2-1600x1066.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Sloan-Canyon-Project-15-2-1600x1066.jpg 1600w, https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Sloan-Canyon-Project-15-2-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Sloan-Canyon-Project-15-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Sloan-Canyon-Project-15-2-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/exiinc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Sloan-Canyon-Project-15-2.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" \/>        <figcaption><\/figcaption>\r\n      <\/figure>\r\n      <div class=\"label\">\r\n        Sloan Canyon Switchyard and Transmission Line        <svg xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"30\" height=\"12.27\" viewBox=\"0 0 30 12.27\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M23.4 0l-1.02 1.1 4.34 4.03H0v2h26.72l-4.34 4.04 